beer.beer_description: A Helles-style lager, the unfiltered nature of the beer aids the development of a light smooth body, while retaining an intense but refined hop aroma. The Helles is straw in colour, full strength with more malt flavour than a typical Australian lager. The addition of the exciting new HPA hop "Vic Secret" as a dry hop adds a modern Australian twist. This hop has imparted an interesting grapefruit and pineapple-like aroma. The light but full flavour of this delicately crafted beer can be enjoyed unfiltered as nature intended.
